Paper: hep-th/9405111

Date: 1994-05-17

Title: Gelfand-Dikii Brackets for Nonstandard Lax Equations

Authors: J.C. Brunelli, Ashok Das and Wen-Jui Huang

Comments: 11 pages, Preprint no. UR1347, ER40685-796

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A9 (1994) 2147-2155

We generalize the construction of Gelfand-Dikii brackets to the case ofnonstandard Lax equations. We also discuss the possible origin of Kac-Moodyalgebras present in such systems.